dct_title_s: Plan A of a section of North Lavallette, Dover Township, Ocean County, New Jersey, owned by Westmont Shore Company
dct_description_sm: This is a map of a plan of North Lavallette in Dover Township. It shows numbered blocks and numbered property lots within those blocks. Major roads are also labelled.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
